{"tid":51662,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那人在日本公廁外草地大便","createTime":"2016-12-23T11:49:53.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-23T15:05:27.000Z","uid":42188,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4a197265bfbfca952e6dc803a59a16e03aad11b1","tid":51662,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T11:49:53.000Z","msg":"微博近日傳出一名中國籍男性遊客，公然蹲在日本長崎縣平和公園草坪上大便的照片。<br />\n<br />\n專門報道中國消息的日本媒體《Record China》，訪問了與該名男遊客乘坐同一客船到訪平和公園的女性拍攝者。拍攝者指事發於12月17日，該名男遊客年約60至70歲。拍攝者指當眾人目睹男遊客「就地解決」時，同行者也不禁譏諷「這太他媽支了」，連導遊也苦惱是初次遇上這種情況，男遊客亦惹來其他遊客及路過的學生的批評。拍攝者不清楚男遊客的背景，但由於草坪不足100米外就有公厠，卻偏偏選擇「就地解決」，拍攝者認為男遊客可能是惡意挑釁。"},{"pid":"54b520babc769c0f3981719dcee7df59a28cdb17","tid":51662,"uid":3818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T11:50:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44320d4a429f8c4447fe5be00d647390a6d02499","tid":51662,"uid":13355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T11:50:47.000Z","msg":"圖定做考子？"},{"pid":"bf94bf7391e370b8c0e1121acca0f20930c6529c","tid":51662,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T11:52:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>圖定做考子？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/23/195155_f847263bf1ab3f2fff0a2ba40fdb4ab5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F23%2F195155_f847263bf1ab3f2fff0a2ba40fdb4ab5.jpg&h=17aaabbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n張圖無乜睇頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24a0500ec73c1926e0f4d94a049a4786ad77a3e6","tid":51662,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T11:52:59.000Z","msg":"冇圖話你老母睇草地大便都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a732a02a